	)

	(text "Sensors\n\nLIS3DHTR (LGA-16) 3-axis accelerometer\n  - VDD / VDD_IO from 3V3 (PSU sheet), 100nF each\n  - I2C1 SCL/SDA <-> STM32 PB6/PB7 (4.7k pull-ups)\n  - SDO/SA0 strap sets I2C address (0x18 / 0x19)\n  - CS tied high (force I2C mode)\n  - INT1 -> STM32 PA2 (EXTI): wake-on-motion\n  - INT2 -> STM32 PA3 (EXTI): tamper / free-fall\n  - RES -> GND per datasheet; ADC1..3 unused (NC)\n\nRole:\n  - Wake the MCU from Stop mode only when handled (INT1)\n  - Tamper policy: optionally zeroize the TOTP secret on\n    motion-while-armed (INT2). See DESIGN.md (Security).\n\nInter-sheet nets: 3V3, GND, I2C1_SCL, I2C1_SDA,\nACC_INT1, ACC_INT2"
